highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Me Porto Bonito” is the highest at #3.
“New Gold (feat. Tame Impala and Bootie Brown)” by Gorillaz, Tame Impala, and Bootie Brown is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #87.
“Feliz Cumpleaños Ferxxo” by Feid is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 62 spots at #93.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 292 weeks straight.
